# Keep the vercel upload set sane (2026-07-09: agent worktrees under .claude/
# ballooned the upload to 2.8GB and broke deploys). Vercel auto-ignores
# node_modules and .git; everything else scratch/non-site goes here.
# NEVER exclude */web/** paths - blog content lives there.
# Patterns are ROOT-ANCHORED (leading /): an unanchored `supabase/` also matched
# Property/web/src/lib/supabase/ and broke the build (module-not-found).
/.claude/
/.cache/
/expense-reconciliation/
/invoicing/
/briefs/
/docs/
/legal/
/supabase/
/optimisation_engine/
/templates/
/_audit_digest.txt
/icaew_extract.txt
/icaew_lines.txt
